author: henning
msg: Move the org.apache.velocity.test package out of the main velocity jar
These unit tests are only useful at compile time because they depend
on a number of external template and test files and increase the size

author: brett
msg: other directories may not be under target

author: henning
msg: for i in java xml properties vm txt xsl vsl jj jjt; do
find . -type f -name \*${i} | grep -v '\.svn' | xargs svn propset svn:eol-style native
on the tree, setting the eol-style for all files named *.java, *.xml,
text files) to the native style of the platform.
This allows Windows and Unix developers not to step on their mutual toes.
